Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:50.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:56.19,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you forever with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:14.68,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}每日从早到晚 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.24,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这样的生活不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:22.33,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.84,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你已泡好热咖啡等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:29.42,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧紧抱住你的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:34.51,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}以前曾屈指等待你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:39.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如今见到你的时间是越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:43.91,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}这样的幸福谁曾料到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:49.52,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}你和我 都堕入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:54.44,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.97,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:09.56,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此情不变
