Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:23.72,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}为何 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:28.89,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我会如此心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:34.85,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}嘴上说 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:38.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}故作冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:40.93,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}嚣张的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}背后是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:47.53,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\be1}最大程度的逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:53.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}为什么呢 泪水不断涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:59.96,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\be1}不敢正视他的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.60,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}明天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:05.45,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}比昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:10.29,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}想比朋友关系更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.96,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}明天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:13.80,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}梦里也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:17.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}恋爱之情更为闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.56,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}Just a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.62,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}Such a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:24.54,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,400)\be1}Still a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:32.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}为何 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:37.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}I can't tell you my heart
