Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新发售 热带健怡苏打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本初登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪·肚脐舔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------AVAN-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是买到了宝贝书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是不是很棒啊 是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 薰怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天保的大饥荒当中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市里打砸抢烧事件接连发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻 这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为米价太高 人民买不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道因为那一吻 她才不来上学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是上课中 请你安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她该不会因为那样而感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真是这样就是我的错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 昨天还那么精神的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你有没打电话给她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我昨晚打电话过去道谢来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没谢成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没人在家 电话没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过碰上这情况 应该都在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心薰么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 才没担心她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 我才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯因为之前没出现过这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还经常炫耀自己体力好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 我真的没担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…没事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定来了学校 只是没去上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我的预想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话 快说你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却很喜欢这季节的天空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我看看你的爷们气概
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天也来图书室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是最近喜欢上读书了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 应该…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 纯一真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到全是字的书 三分钟就犯困
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这么夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天来图书室的真正理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对梨穗子说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 有没看到薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 棚町怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没看见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才听高桥老师说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰今天是无故缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 老师打电话到她家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎昨晚彻夜未归
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问我知不知道内情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…橘 你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课不上了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便帮我编个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 像没头苍蝇似的到处转也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 有没有特别喜欢的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有 当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是冬季限定的白雪巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有新发售的可可味雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真喜欢新东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是限定物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到只有现在才能吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会忍不住买了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意别吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你买好今年的冬衣了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你准备得还真周全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高人气店的新款外套
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9月就已经完售谢礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 秋天时买还会送礼品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看中了就要赶紧入手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是穿衣打扮的铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先确定一下规则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟往常一样 玩九球制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 旗开得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺强的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 为啥我会这么担心薰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么跟我一起就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了母女俩一起努力的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是昨天很帅气的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不是吵架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭女生可是最差劲的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 刚才在湖边哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 就算觉得自己没错也要道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我会这么担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像花式溜冰一样 嗖地一声就滑跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还唰一声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到从厨房端出来时 就觉得很危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为蟹壳像这样晃来晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 就差一步了 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然掉到了地上 我倒也没受什么伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着那样道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个劲地低头道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奶汁烤菜浇到你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定用餐的时候 会借那里的制服穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能看到响的女招待打扮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的浇在身上 我也不会穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来那个店员 是我们学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是二年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 「来自北方的蟹奶汁烤菜」味道真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那道 「朴蕈菇和风意面」味道很一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点「来自北方的蟹奶汁烤菜」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复客人点的单超难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏这时候 身上只有这点钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 只有在这里等她下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛去了 担心死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要你来担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等我个十五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到休息时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她人 算是放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 她果然出了什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫的 注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我不是过来闲晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你昨天去哪儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且没去上学 却来打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…不能给店里添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你无故缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师很担心 打电话去你家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你妈妈说你昨晚跑了出去就没回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底去哪了 干啥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去漫画咖啡屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经那么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为只要母女俩齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能好好过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我去打工的路上 碰到了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟一个陌生的男人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家从没见过她那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会很火大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽了力去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不成为妈妈的负担 拼命地打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却因为这个大吵了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说在考虑再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托能不能别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫 洗衣服 我一次都没偷懒过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有时还会做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来证明我们两个完全能过上好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会敷衍了事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要什么新爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话 我只能跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本还想冷静地跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 眼泪还是流了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭就哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 总有些表情不想让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要对自己逼得太紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭就哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭并不代表你软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你把母亲的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有与父亲的回忆看得比自己还重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么清楚我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？因为…我们打交道久嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然心里也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈其实也没有忘掉爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了 不知道自己该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是用不着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说你不需要就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在身边的话 会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打个电话给妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事 回去以后会好好问你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚开始超级生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最后笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔为之也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊 有红蓝绿三种颜色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 还有绿色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道有三种颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就不知道是哪几种颜色了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右耳形状是不一样的 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不同么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 右耳比较圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左耳有点儿撑出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也你呢 要什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色吧 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小逢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么颜色都行 中多你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要蓝色…蓝色行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那我要绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那就定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天见 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季限定 超级白雪巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都会在你身边 帮你打气的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 现在的我肯定超有型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然会有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在身边的话 会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她只是从初中开始打交道的损友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 明明啥都不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的…喜欢上她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 还在泡着么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥 看起来很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要帮一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦 帮大忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你竟然会拿讲义 太令人意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实刚才被老师抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后叫我拿第一堂课要用的讲义过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就乖乖答应了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～今天心情很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的话应该撒腿就跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天翘了课 要补过～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了 快回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聊天的话 边走边聊也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有精神就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 老是闷闷不乐也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没勉强自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就是说你一个人也拿得了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 不是说了帮我拿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全复活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 下午翘课可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 当中有点缘由…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是我的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话 拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 测验也快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也得借给棚町
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你尽快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那家伙翘了一天的课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 进展
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.43,0:24:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 之后是不是很快就找到棚町了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 为啥你会知道
